<h1>Renter Insight</h1>

<p>Dear <%=@user.first_name %>,</p>

<p>You have a new message <%="from " + @communication.from.name if @communication.from.present? %>:</p>

<p><strong><%=raw(@communication.body.gsub("\n", "<br>")) %></strong></p>

<p>You can respond to this email, or reply in the <a href="<%=SystemMailer.base_url %>/communications/#comment-<%=@communication.hash_id %>">Renter Insight Portal</a></p>

<p>Thank you,<br>
  Renter Insight</p>
